text: Diamond Dogs is a 2007 Canadian Chinese action movie directed by Dolph Lundgren (who also stars) and Shimon Dotan. It also stars Yu Nan, Raicho Vasilev, Zhang Chunnian. It was released direct to DVD in North America. ==Other websites== * * Category:2007 action movies Category:Canadian action movies Category:Chinese movies Category:Movies set in China Category:Movies set in Mongolia Category:Movies directed by Dolph Lundgren Category:Movies directed by Shimon Dotan
